Subject: [PATCH] drm/amd/display: Blank phantom OTG before enabling
References: bsc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 6.6.3
Git-commit: e87a6c5b7780b5f423797351eb586ed96cc6d151

[ Upstream commit e87a6c5b7780b5f423797351eb586ed96cc6d151 ]

[Description]
Before enabling the phantom OTG for an update we
must enable DPG to avoid underflow.

